---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact | LetsFixIndia" description="Contact LetsFixIndia about corrections, research collaboration, or the public record.">
  <div class="page-shell"><header class="record-header"><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h1>Help make the record more accurate.</h1><p class="lede">For a correction or a new source, the structured review form is the fastest way to help. For collaboration, contact the maintainer directly.</p></header>
    <div class="feature-grid section"><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span><h3>Correction desk</h3><p>Use the review form for source-backed corrections, court updates, or missing public records.</p><a href="/submit">Send a correction →</a></article><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">@</span><h3>Research or collaboration</h3><p>For editorial or research collaboration, write to the project maintainer.</p><a href="mailto:workwithdevit@gmail.com">workwithdevit@gmail.com →</a></article><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">⌘</span><h3>Inspect the project</h3><p>The code and published data can be inspected by contributors and reviewers.</p><a href="https://github.com/basithladdu/letsfixindia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open GitHub ↗</a></article></div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
